A general thrusting motion of the [[pelvic]] region, generally related to [[sexual symbols]].  It is commonly used as a sign of wanting to have [[sex]] with another. See [[Time Warp]].

It is also a sign of victory against another individual. The game [[Unreal Tournament]] has the option of performing a pelvic thrust in multiplayer games.

Also used in chat, such as IRC, to express dominance in something.

*Eaiis: I have rolled a 5. This defeats your 4.
*Eaiis: *pelvic thrusts*

There is also a popular [[internet]] image of a [[Imperial stormtrooper|stormtrooper]] performing a pelvic thrust.